<section class="cta">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-content">
      <div class="cta-glow"></div>
      <h2>20 ans d'IT. <span class="text-gradient">L'IA en plus.</span></h2>
      <p>On ne découvre pas votre métier — on le comprend, on l'automatise, et on vous rend autonomes.</p>
      <div class="cta-actions">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
          Discuter de votre projet
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:contact@bubblestone.ai" class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg">
          Nous écrire
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="cta-note">Diagnostic gratuit • Sans engagement</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta {
    padding: var(--spacing-3xl) 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .cta::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-white) 0%, var(--color-gray-50) 100%);
    z-index: -1;
  }

  .cta-content {
    position: relative;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    padding: var(--spacing-2xl);
    background: var(--color-white);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    overflow: hidden;
    z-index: 100;
    transition: border-color 0.5s ease, box-shadow 0.5s ease;
  }

  .cta-content.line-reached {
    border-color: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.5);
    box-shadow:
      0 0 20px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3),
      0 0 40px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15),
      0 0 60px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.05);
  }

  .cta-glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: -100px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 400px;
    height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .cta-content > p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-600);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .cta-actions {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .cta-note {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-gray-400);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cta-content {
      padding: var(--spacing-xl) var(--spacing-md);
    }

    .cta-actions {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .cta-actions .btn {
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
